						<h1>
															Creating a local folder in Thunderbird									</h1>
			
																
				
					<div style='font-size:12px; color:#aaa; margin-bottom:-10px; padding-top:5px;'>
							<div style='float:left; margin-right:20px;'><span style='color:#606060;'>Written by Jacob Nicholson</div>
							<div style='float:left; margin-right:20px;'><span style='color:#606060;'>Views:</span> <span name='page_views' id='page_views'>19,391</span></div>
							<div style='float:left; margin-right:20px;' title='Originally published: Oct 9, 2012'><span style='color:#606060;'>Published:</span> Jul 4, 2014</div>
							<div style='float:left; margin-right:20px;'><span style='color:#606060;'>Comments:</span> <a href='#comments'>21</a></div>
							<div style='clear:both;'></div>
						</div>
						</div>
		
	
		

	

								<p>You can create a local folder in Thunderbird to archive messages from the server into. This allows you to reduce disk-space used by an e-mail account on the server, and to help prevent <a href="http://www.inmotionhosting.com/support/email/email-troubleshooting/imap-resource-usage" target="_blank">resource usage issues when using IMAP</a>.</p>

<ol class="article_list">
  <li><a class="std_ss" href="//cdn.inmotionhosting.com/support/images/stories/email/imap-folders/Thunderbird-local-create.png"><img  style="width: 200px; float: right; margin: -3px 0px 0px 0px;" src="//cdn.inmotionhosting.com/support/images/stories/email/imap-folders/Thunderbird-local-create.png" alt="Thunderbird-local-create" /></a>
    <strong>Right-click</strong> on <strong>Local Folders</strong> and select <strong>New Folder...</strong><div style="clear: both;"></div></li>
  
  <li><a class="std_ss" href="//cdn.inmotionhosting.com/support/images/stories/email/imap-folders/Thunderbird-new-folder.png"><img  style="width: 200px; float: right; margin: -3px 0px 0px 0px;" src="//cdn.inmotionhosting.com/support/images/stories/email/imap-folders/Thunderbird-new-folder.png" alt="Thunderbird-new-folder" /></a>
    Give your new folder a name
    <div style="clear: both;"></div></li>
  
  <li><a class="std_ss" href="//cdn.inmotionhosting.com/support/images/stories/email/imap-folders/Thunderbird-move-to-local.png"><img  style="width: 300px; float: right;" src="//cdn.inmotionhosting.com/support/images/stories/email/imap-folders/Thunderbird-move-to-local.png" alt="Thunderbird-move-to-local" /></a>
    <p><strong>OPTIONAL:</strong></p>
    <p>Select your messages to archive</p>
    <p><strong>Right-click</strong> and choose</p>
    <p><strong>Move To &gt; Local Folders &gt; Your folder's name</strong></p><div style="clear: both;"></div></li>
</ol> 
	
						 </div>

	






